 - `bq76952_soc.h` / `.cpp`: ancillary SoC estimation and persisted learned-capacity state.
 - `bq76952_controls.h`: parented switch/button declarations.
-- `bq76952.h` / `.cpp`: ESPHome lifecycle and entity publication.
+- `bq76952.h` / `.cpp`: ESPHome connection state and entity publication.
 - `test_config.yaml`: pinned compile fixture for the full component surface.
